title: Crew Show! (24 Hr of Lemons)
description: Fresh off the track at Infineon Raceway for 24 Hours of Lemons we try our first video webcast and discuss the new Cadillac CTS, shoe protection, the new G63 AMG, used M3s and we compare luxury sport sedans.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
